51:23.960 --> 51:26.680
What joy, eh? Creates joy!

51:27.240 --> 51:29.424
Such a great thing! It's a collective.

51:29.625 --> 51:32.320
Marriage has to be collective, then it is sustained.

51:32.520 --> 51:34.840
It has to be collective. Indians know this trick.

51:35.080 --> 51:37.400
You see, they have a collective marriage.

51:37.600 --> 51:39.360
Everything has to be in the marriage;

51:39.560 --> 51:42.873
even the reeves of the village, even the barber,

51:43.074 --> 51:45.682
even the washerman, everybody is to be there,

51:45.883 --> 51:47.640
has to work out something for the marriage.

51:47.840 --> 51:50.000
So the whole community is there to marry

51:50.200 --> 51:52.482
and that's how the marriage you see is there

51:52.683 --> 51:55.120
because everybody looks after you, you see?

51:55.320 --> 51:57.280
If there are many forces on one point

51:57.480 --> 51:59.280
then the point remains where it is.

51:59.480 --> 52:01.371
Doesn't shift, you see?

52:01.572 --> 52:03.840
So there is no shifting in marriage.

52:04.630 --> 52:07.734
Equal and opposite forces always acting on one point,

52:07.935 --> 52:09.745
you better be there.

