54:32.720 --> 54:34.960
it keeps its flame burning.

54:35.200 --> 54:36.880
And you do everything to keep it,

54:37.080 --> 54:39.605
because once it is out again it will be difficult to enlighten,

54:39.806 --> 54:40.840
